debian-doctor (1.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release
  * Comprehensive system diagnostic and troubleshooting tool
  * System health checks for disk, memory, network, and services
  * Interactive diagnosis with fix suggestions
  * File permission analysis tool
  * Comprehensive system reporting with health scores
  * Simple text-based interface for universal compatibility
  * CLI mode for specific issue diagnosis
  * Automated fix execution with safety checks
  * Support for both user and root operation modes

